Flutter is a declarative UI framework and not a imperative one. You will not imperativitly create the new field.

The Flutter (declarative) way of doing this is when clicking a button change the state of your widget and call setState, when the widget is rebuild it will take in considerations your change on the state and it will build your new component. To sumarize you can do something like this:

